Package io.papermc.paper.registry.data

Interface BannerPatternRegistryEntry.Builder

All Superinterfaces:
BannerPatternRegistryEntry, RegistryBuilder<PatternType>
Enclosing interface:
BannerPatternRegistryEntry
@Experimental @NonExtendable public static interface BannerPatternRegistryEntry.Builder extends BannerPatternRegistryEntry, RegistryBuilder<PatternType>
A mutable builder for the BannerPatternRegistryEntry plugins may change in applicable registry events.

The following values are required for each builder:

  • assetId(Key)
  • translationKey(String)
